    					<img src="/web/20110209231545im_/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/images/misc/quote_icon2.png" alt="Quote" /> Originally Posted by <strong>Duke-of-Waterloo</strong>
    					<a href="/web/20110209231545/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/showthread.php?p=5935#post5935" rel="nofollow"><img class="inlineimg" src="/web/20110209231545im_/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/images/buttons/viewpost-right.png" alt="View Post" /></a>
